content: darwintree: Made significant contributions with two merged PRs: fixing model endpoint override issues (#446) and adding the Conflux plugin (#481), which was the largest PR at +2769 lines. Worked primarily on feature development (53%) and bug fixes (33%), modifying 241 files with +14K/-11K lines across 15 commits. Currently has two open PRs including a fix for parameter issues in generateObjectV2 (#445) and created issue #469 (now closed) related to the same functionality.
